OL,3,CMan who killed his mum caught after
OL,4,Conline gamer from US called UK police
OL,6,FA man who had a history of violence
OL,7,Ftowards his mother and had threatened
OL,8,Fto kill her multiple times has been
OL,9,Fjailed for life for her murder.
OL,11,FDebra Cantrell's body was found in an
OL,12,Fadvanced state of decomposition at a
OL,13,Fproperty in Colwill Road, Plymouth, on
OL,14,F31 May last year.
OL,16,FIt is believed she was killed around
OL,17,Fthree weeks earlier, murdered by her
OL,18,Fson Callum Thomas.
