OL,3,CMan who killed his mum caught after
OL,4,Conline gamer from US called UK police
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall Police found Ms
OL,7,FCantrell's body after an online gamer
OL,8,Ffrom the North Carolina called them
OL,9,Fand reported a concern for welfare.
OL,11,FHe told detectives he had received a
OL,12,Fcall from Thomas on 8 May last year.
OL,13,FPolice say he had killed his mother
OL,14,Fthe day before.
OL,16,FLater that month, when an mutual
OL,17,Ffriend told the North Carolina caller
OL,18,Fhe could not get hold of Thomas, the
OL,19,Fonline gamer decided to contact UK
OL,20,Fpolice.
