OL,6,FAs a result, police went to Colwill
OL,7,FRoad in Plymouth where they found Ms
OL,8,FCantrell's remains. She died as a
OL,9,Fresult of a stab wound to the chest.
OL,11,FThomas denied murder but was convicted
OL,12,Ffollowing a trial at Plymouth Crown
OL,13,FCourt. The jury found him guilty by a
OL,14,Fmajority verdict.
OL,16,FThe 33-year-old was sentenced to life
OL,17,Fin prison with a a minimum of 12
OL,18,Fyears, less time already served.
