OL,6,FA spokesperson for the family said:
OL,7,F"Debs will be missed by family and
OL,8,Ffriends.
OL,10,F"We would like to thank the police and
OL,11,Fother agencies for the support we have
OL,12,Freceived over the past 13 months."
OL,14,FThere was an extensive history of
OL,15,Fdomestic violence between the
OL,16,Fdefendant and his mother going back
OL,17,Fmore than 10 years. During that time,
OL,18,FThomas had threatened to kill his
OL,19,Fmother on several occasions.
