OL,6,FThe judge acknowledged that Thomas had
OL,7,Fproblems with his mental health and
OL,8,Fthat there was no suggestion that he
OL,9,Fhad planned to kill his mother.
OL,11,FBut he also said that the relationship
OL,12,Fbetween Thomas and his mother had been
OL,13,F"tempestuous and volatile" and that he
OL,14,Fhad been violent towards her in the
OL,15,Fpast.
