OL,6,FDetective Inspector Neil Blanchard
OL,7,Fsaid: "This has been a complex
OL,8,Finvestigation and I would like to
OL,9,Fthank all those who have been involved
OL,10,Fand provided their expertise to allow
OL,11,Fus to prosecute this case, including
OL,12,Four colleagues in the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service.
OL,15,F"Debra's family and friends have had
OL,16,Fto endure a tragic loss and I hope
OL,17,Fthat this verdict and sentence brings
OL,18,Fthem some measure of closure and are
OL,19,Fnow able to go on with their lives."
